  * src/background_process.c, src/lancode.c, src/lancode.h, src/qtcutil.c,
  src/qtcutil.h, src/qtcwin.c, src/readqtccalls.c: New feature: QTC flags
  sending through LAN to another nodes, when user mark a callsign.

